Interface Seeable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJavaDoc, JavaDocAttribute, JavaDocClass, JavaDocMethod

    public interface Seeable
    If JavaDoc element can have @code{see} annotation, has to implement this interface.

    Stepan Cais, scais@kiv.zcu.cz, 6.12.2012
